INSERT INTO `tag_essay` VALUES(176, 1, 75, 0, '\n"The news media is a reliable source of unbiased information.\n\n"', '"Some people think that the news media is a reliable source of unbiased information. However, in my opinion, since there are many stakeholders of it and news makers have to consider populace’s interests, the news media have no choice but to going to biased direction.\n\nFirstly, a broadcasting station which broadcast the news has lots of stakeholders, resulting in familiar relationship with a market. It makes people in the media act partially, leading the stakeholders beneficial and advantageous. The studies have shown that according to contents of the news, the price of the stockmarket is volatile. People can easily see the example of it before the presidential election. According to types of stations, there are definitely different news of candidates which in one station, is better than expected and in other station, can’t be worse than the news about one candidate. It relates to stocks of each candidates.\n\nOn top of that, makers of the news media need to consider mass’s interests, which means that they contain a part of the issues of our society. This is because the news media is also mass media whose life is up to populace’s choices. For example, in these days there are a lot of crime news which often are unkind and crucial, even if actual crime rate is not high like that according to the researches. This is because most of people want to watch stimulating information.\n\nTo sum up, since there are lots of people who relate to the stock of the news and makers have to think about their audience, the news media is not a trustful source of unbiased information."', '', '', '', '', 0, 0, 'essay', 'Tagging', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00');
